    <div class="container">
      <h2>Questions Sherman Oaks Customers Ask</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you offer same-day appliance repair in Sherman Oaks, CA?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Our technicians cover all of Sherman Oaks — Mulholland Drive hillside, Ventura Blvd corridor, and all ZIP codes 91401, 91403, 91411, and 91423. Call before noon for same-day afternoon service.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you repair Jenn-Air appliances in Sherman Oaks?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Jenn-Air column refrigerators, French door units, pro-style ranges, and panel-ready dishwashers are common throughout Sherman Oaks 91423. We carry OEM Jenn-Air parts and know the specific failure patterns on these models.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you repair Gaggenau appliances in Sherman Oaks?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Gaggenau steam combination ovens, Vario cooktops, and dishwashers require specific technical knowledge and OEM parts. We're trained on Gaggenau systems and carry parts for the most common failures.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Does LADWP hard water affect appliances in Sherman Oaks?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. LADWP runs 230–310 mg/L throughout Sherman Oaks — including in luxury Jenn-Air and Gaggenau appliances. We check for LADWP mineral deposits proactively on every relevant call.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Are you available on weekends in Sherman Oaks?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Saturday 8am–7pm and Sunday 9am–5pm.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">What is your diagnostic fee in Sherman Oaks?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Our diagnostic fee is $89, waived when you proceed with the repair. Written estimate before we start. Most Sherman Oaks repairs run $150–$500.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you also serve Encino, Studio City, and Van Nuys?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Our Sherman Oaks service extends to Encino, Studio City, North Hollywood, Van Nuys, Tarzana, and all of the San Fernando Valley.</div></details>
